<TEXT>
<P>
   There is carnage in America's cinemas these days, and not all of
it is on the screen.
</P>
<P>
   Having built far more cinemas in recent years than the market
can sustain, the big chains of movie theatres are leaking cash and
watching their share prices crash through the floor.
</P>
