on Dave Letterman's show the other night, exuding warmth and wit,
yet she refuses any substantial news interview in New York, where
she's supposed to be running for the U.S. Senate. This is bad for
democracy and it's bad for anybody who believes that people have a
right to information that will better enable them to govern
themselves. By DAN LYNCH.
