PLANT STRAWBERRIES THE EASY WAY
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
 
 
By CAROL BIDWELL 
c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Get a head start on your spring garden with Triumph Plant Co.'s
new Hanging Basket Strawberry Kit, which will be available
beginning in early February in KMart, Wal-mart and Target stores as
well as local garden centers.
</P>
<P>
   A kit includes three ever-bearing strawberry plants and coconut
fiber soil plus an all-weather hanging basket. The berries can be
grown on a porch or patio or even inside, hanging in a sunny
window. A three-plant kit retails for $5.99. &QL;
