<P>
   ATLANTA _ Last year Atlanta went to the Super Bowl. This year
the Super Bowl comes to Atlanta! The official NFL site for kids,
www.playfootball.com, offers fun football facts and up-to-date info
on the teams that could play in the Jan. 30 game. You can vote in
