<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FEATURE-BUDGET-ART-BOS </SLUG>
  
 ART ADV.: Photos SCI-VISION and PIANO-TEACHER, and a graphic with
SCI-VISION are being transmitted to NYT Photo Service
subscribers.  
 For Immediate Release  
 
